3.10	Steve_Cochran_(radio_host)	Steve Cochran (radio host)	Steve Cochran (born March 14, 1961) is an American radio broadcaster. Steve presently hosts a radio show from 5pm-7pm on WIND AM 560 in Chicago, 10am-12pm and 6pm-9pm on KTRS 550 AM in St. Louis. He previously worked for WGN radio in Chicago from 2000 to 2010.	
